---
layout: layouts/tool.njk
title: Regex Tester & Debugger
description: Free online regex tester and debugger. Test regular expressions in real-time with match highlighting, capture groups, and pattern explanations.
keywords: regex tester, regular expression tester, regex debugger, regex101 alternative, test regex online, regex pattern matcher
permalink: /tools/regex-tester/
toolId: regex-tester
toolJs: regex-tester.js
ogImage: regex-tester.jpg
---
{# Get tool data from tools.json #}
{% set toolData = tools | findById(toolId) %}

{% block schema %}
<!-- Schema.org BreadcrumbList -->
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
